<div id="post-1186" class="blog-post position-6 even-post"><div class="even-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/ponto-por-ponto/blog-audiovisual/ato-na-assembleia-legislativa-sobre-o-ai5-digital">Ato na Assembleia Legislativa sobre o AI5 Digital</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">Maggio 20, 2009 0:00</span><span class="author">, by Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/ponto-por-ponto/blog-audiovisual/ato-na-assembleia-legislativa-sobre-o-ai5-digital#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>no comments yet</span></a></span></span><p style="text-align: center;">
